      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i hear you but i'm also looking at my cabinets and i have some cipro left over from a UTI i had a few months ago. since that's an antibiotic it should be way safer for a sinus infection than a decongestant right? if i just take a couple of doses to clear this up it shouldn't be a problem should it?",
